Text: Re Questionnaire Cc below attached is the contract review questionnaire Wade Stubblefield PM To Misty ES cc Rogers ct Don ES Tim nronXGate Kevin M CT Vladimir nronXGate Wes nronXGate Berney C CT Subject Questionnaire Misty Can you please send the ccd individuals above the complete contract review questionnaire for their review and information Also can you have a brief minute meeting set up with Berney Aucoin and Vladimir Gorny to walk through the database functionality as it exists today It will probably be several weeks before that aspect of the project if more fully addressed but I want them to at least be familiar with where we are today and what additional questions we might have about functionality You should probably make sure that the IT programmer is present at the meeting Thanks Wade
